add

public boolean add(Change change)
Add change to list, if it meets the following criteria:
  • Not already on list (see Change.equals(Object) for details)
  • The Change.Operation must not be empty
  • The Change.Operation must not conflict with what is already on the list

getRequiredProperties

public java.util.List<java.lang.String> getRequiredProperties()
Get names of all extended settings the values of which are required to process the list of changes. This additional information is required if an extended setting is hidden (i.e. its value is not displayed when retrieving the currently defined values) but shall be partially changed (with Change.Operation.addAppend or Change.Operation.removePart ).

Returns:
List of required extended settings
